text: Bought a bra from jurong point lady ask me several time on the size I want told her multiple times and yet she still took the wrong size n now the band is too big! If too small can still put extension now too big what am I supposed to do and the bras are not cheap also!! Wrote in and no reply also so irresponsible!! If can will give -100 stars for service!
The shop assistants were extremely friendly and knowledgeable!
